            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1422047321,
            "creation_date": 1422047321,
            "body": "<p>In java 8 using stream<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] array=new String[]{\"a\",\"b\",\"c\",\"a\"};\nMap&lt;String,Integer&gt; map1=Arrays.stream(array).collect(Collectors.toMap(x-&gt;x,x-&gt;1,(key,value)-&gt;value+1));\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
